default4.5
default              
defaultThe ma
defaultin purpose is to trial an innovative project to mitigate rural isolation and improve access to essential services through the creation of a community hub. 
defaultThis hub is likely to be the accepted market town for the area with a number of locations within it p
defaultroviding a set of accessible services. These may or may not be co-located depending on natural affinities
default.
default 
defaultSST has identified a number of services that could be delivered more locally, such as Health Clinics, Further Education and Training, Citizens Advice Bureau and Community/Social Housing services.  
default4.6
default              
defaultThe SST will work with the District and County Council
defaults, health and education partners, community facilitators and housing associations to develop a local community package of services that could be provided through this community hub.  
