default              
defaultThere is a need to address the disparity between urban and rural areas in respect of the bus pass
default. One option (that’s currently not permitted under th
defaulte 
defaultConcessionary Fare Scheme)
default that we often encounter in feedback from the community is that 
defaulta small flat fare could be levied for bus pass use. The monies raised 
defaultcould then be used to extend the scheme.
