default6.5
default              
defaultThere is also a 
defaultneed to
default develop services that people will use – ie they go where they need to go when people want them to.
default&#xa0;
default We need to get more flexibility from agencies and services that people go 
defaultto make
default it easier.
default&#xa0;
default For example, more ability to pick appointments in hospitals; 
defaultgrouping services so that in one trip to town, someone can achieve lots of tasks.
